subSubSection.paragraph:
STC with curved row of long teeth; ITC curved (
Fig. 10C
). Spinnerets: PMS white; PLS, slenderness, basal, distal end white (
Fig. 10E
). PMS 1.66 long, 0.53 wide; PLS 7.41 long (2.50, 2.14, 2.77); PMS–PMS 2.13.
